&lt;p&gt;Three the biggest things which Bharat gave to the world  &lt;br&gt;
but even our own people don&amp;rsquo;t understand these fully.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A. Tantra : A way to control your own life energy. Live your every breath. Live life in totality and without duality. Hundreds of Agama Tantra Shastra defines them but unfortunately this is the most misunderstood work of Bharat. Whoever tries to speak boldly on this is either sidelined or he does something nasty and people do not listen to him. Finally it remained in the hands of those who cannot communicate it to the world.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
